\par\plain\f2\fs24\b0\i0\plain{\f2\fs24\b0\i0 Here\rquote s how you tie your plot-related story elements (scenes and problems) together: Pick a beat you want to identify, and click on }{\f3\fs24\b1\i0 Show Problems/Scenes}{\f2\fs24\b0\i0  to display a list of your outline\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2
\rquote s problems and scenes. Select the problem or scene, and drag it to the beat\rquote s drop area, the box which reads \lquote No element Selected\rquote :}
\par\plain\f2\fs24\b0\i0
