\par\pard\plain\tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\ltrch\loch{\f2\fs24\b0\i0 Remember that a beat sheet is a pattern for your plotting, and once you pick it, you\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2 \rquote re freezing an aspect of your story structure. This is especially important when dealing with subplot integration.}}